OL,3,CWoman detained in hospital after
OL,4,Cstabbing two boys aged 10
OL,6,FA woman who stabbed two 10-year-old
OL,7,Fboys has been detained in hospital
OL,8,Findefinitely.
OL,10,FThe boys were attacked at a property
OL,11,Fin Fold Hill, Friskney, near Skegness,
OL,12,Fduring a stand-off with police after
OL,13,Fofficers were called to carry out a
OL,14,Fwelfare check on 29 November 2022.
OL,16,FAnn Marie McEvoy, 42, who was arrested
OL,17,Fat the scene, was initially charged
OL,18,Fwith two offences of attempted murder.
