OL,6,FBut she was later deemed unfit to
OL,7,Fstand trial after a court heard she
OL,8,Fwas suffering from a mental disability.
OL,10,FInstead a trial of the facts was held
OL,11,Fin June to determine whether she
OL,12,Fcarried out the alleged acts.
OL,14,FA jury unanimously found McEvoy,
OL,15,Fformerly of Church Walk, Colchester,
OL,16,Fhad committed two counts of wounding
OL,17,Fthe boys with intent.
