OL,3,CWoman detained in hospital after
OL,4,Cstabbing two boys aged 10
OL,6,FThe trial heard McEvoy had been found
OL,7,Fby police in a bedroom holding a large
OL,8,Fkitchen knife, with the two boys lying
OL,9,Fon the bed and bleeding from their
OL,10,Finjuries.
OL,12,FShe was arrested after being tasered
OL,13,Fand fell to the ground.
OL,15,FOne of the boys had stab wounds to his
OL,16,Fchest, neck and back. The other boy
OL,17,Fhad a wound on his right hand, neck
OL,18,Fand arm.
