OL,3,CWoman detained in hospital after
OL,4,Cstabbing two boys aged 10
OL,6,FFirearms officer PC Andrew Donnelly
OL,7,Ftold the court: "One of the children
OL,8,Fwas underneath the duvet and another
OL,9,Fwas further away but looking at me.
OL,10,FBoth boys were crying."
OL,12,FThe court heard one of the boys had
OL,13,Fwoken up to find McEvoy on the bed
OL,14,Fwith a knife above her head.
OL,16,FOne of the boys said in a statement:
OL,17,F"She went for (Boy B) first, got his
OL,18,Fback, nearly got his heart but I
OL,19,Fstopped it."
