OL,3,CWoman detained in hospital after
OL,4,Cstabbing two boys aged 10
OL,6,FMcEvoy was not present for the
OL,7,Fsentencing hearing at Lincoln Crown
OL,8,FCourt on Wednesday as she remains at a
OL,9,Fmental hospital in Essex for treatment.
OL,11,FThe court heard she was suffering from
OL,12,Fa schizoaffective disorder.
OL,14,FJudge Simon Hirst made an order to
OL,15,Fdetain McEvoy in hospital until
OL,16,Fdoctors believe she is safe to be
OL,17,Freleased.
